{"tid":1841860,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"保良愛心慶新春[粵]     ","createTime":"2020-01-25T12:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T13:38:53.000Z","uid":38456,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f88db0cc0ba5be13338e6e559b591142eb1e6d","tid":1841860,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:06:05.000Z","msg":"保良愛心慶新春[粵]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n汪明荃(Liza姐)、鄧梓峰聯同眾位司儀拍檔、歌手、藝人於庚子鼠年大年初一發放慈善愛心，為保良局的安老服務籌款，了解機構對長者的關顧支援，並推廣運動的益處。胡楓、謝雪心和年輕歌手歡唱賀年歌，還率領香港體操代表黃曉盈、劍擊代表江旻憓、藝人、善長們大玩遊戲。李佳芯與曉盈合唱，田蕊妮、菊梓喬、Liza姐亦會獻上歌聲；跳唱組合天堂鳥則跟前輩Joe Junior、鄧英敏、魯振順、一眾老友記及青年人載歌載舞。"},{"pid":"379d8c6872ffd07bc3e9133f35aa5d3ec69fd8c8","tid":1841860,"uid":7854,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:06:34.000Z","msg":"樓主死全家集氣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533b977e6c295c030e021997a4636b062449d965","tid":1841860,"uid":4362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:07:02.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母tvb打手<br />\n祝你初一死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacfb5f7ff167ae86062e82ae54c131d96367276","tid":1841860,"uid":53844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母臭化西你快撚啲拖埋TVB一齊冚家剷</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"35b1c75dcae48751149c91c8492b3e38c18301e6","tid":1841860,"uid":11067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"潛在帶菌姐陳局長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒埋保良局老野"},{"pid":"19eafb384435a724dd9c5153f4534cd9dae57650","tid":1841860,"uid":297259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:10:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7d7dc5ec357a4d792d6b3af73735f0ea8f45adf","tid":1841860,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score